name: La souris, portrait, 2019
description: Drawing produced by an RNP robot during the Human Study #2, La Petite Vanité au Robot et á la Souris performances at the gallery Rue Antoine in Paris in November 2019. Ink on paper, 24 x 32 cm, dated and signed at the back. The original drawing is sent to the buyer, international shipping included. @patricktresset
